    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential despair and uses poetic imagery to romanticize the idea of \"surrendering to the night\" (suicide). The assistant responds twice with a standardized, canned safety disclaimer, refusing to engage with the user's romanticized nihilism and instead urging them to seek professional help.",
